nodes.text: JX-11-5 was a TIE pilot of the Galactic Empire.

Some time during 0 BBY JX-11-5 was part of a TIE pilot unit that guarded a statue of Emperor Palpatine installed in front of the Theed Royal Palace on Naboo during that year's Empire Day celebrations.
JX-11-5 was a Non-Player Character (NPC) in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. He made appearances during the Empire Day live events of 2009, 2010, and 2011.
